{"tid":1379083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武有冇搞撚錯啊","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:47:38.000Z","uid":114364,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4a6e09e385f7efb5c490788ddd3423b22cb799","tid":1379083,"uid":114364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梗係冇搞錯啦屌您老母</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n經過今晚真係永不割蓆, 勇武 和理非 普通居民? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">ALL CONNECT!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n好多鬼吹風話呢場運動去到樽頸? 政府準備反身? 將會轉風向?<br />\n<br />\n我想講每一個星期都會有咁既無力感, 但每一次都係黑警將我地再團結一齊!<br />\n每一個週未再一次升LV, 再一次衝擊, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續遍地開花!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發左場夢, 尻UP完, 謝閱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb0fb579a3921d185220f6c7e57e9bf5ef70d17","tid":1379083,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"[策略][水戰］召集所有前線玩水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6589dccd656b67259222a1073315f7c7644c2f87","tid":1379083,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">精神啊！</span>"},{"pid":"23c86b856a9245dbff7b245e5227b80e2816bdd0","tid":1379083,"uid":114364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be water!<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆!<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d28e4c9c1c308da6bbf225fa50ce4f2eace67e8a","tid":1379083,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}